original_title: k.d. lang - Ingénue Redux - Live From the Majestic Theatre
overview: k.d. lang performs at the legendary Majestic Theatre in San Antonio, Texas following an unforgettable tour celebrating the 25th anniversary of the GRAMMY award-winning, critically acclaimed album "Ingenue". This special concert features the entire "Ingenue" album (including her hit "Constant Craving"), along with classics from her 2004 album "Hymns of the 49th Parallel.
title: k.d. lang - Ingénue Redux - Live From the Majestic Theatre
